@noindent
This is the first release of the SST package@.
The package includes a C library and a Java library@.
The libraries are closely related, and the Java library will use the C
library in the future@.
Some features are not yet implemented or will be redesigned, but other
features are mostly stable, including:

@itemize
@item
Status codes that can be used for function return values@.

@item
Exception classes that correspond to the failure status codes@.

@item
Functions for performing bitwise operations with bit granularity@.

@item
Functions for parsing GNU-style command-line options@.

@item
Wrappers to smooth out various features of other libraries@.
@end itemize
